description.en:
Mei Hanamaki, a second-year high school student who has transferred to another school for some reason. It was Iku Hinosaka, a handsome sergeant who is the most popular girl in the school, who showed her natural nature and took the seat next to her, who seemed to be floating from the first day of transfer.
The cool Iku's de S is mercilessly poured on Mei, and each other's first impression is the worst.
However, the relationship between the two began to change as a result of something ...!? The super popular school romantic comedy, which won first place in the magical i Land novel overall ranking, has become a long-awaited comic!
